WEBVTT

00:00:04.149 --> 00:00:08.195 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Some of the greatest joys we experience in life

00:00:08.195 --> 00:00:11.907 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
are a result of a happy family life.

00:00:11.907 --> 00:00:14.910 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But living in these hectic last days,

00:00:14.910 --> 00:00:18.038 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
achieving such happiness is very difficult.

00:00:18.038 --> 00:00:21.709 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The Governing Body
deeply appreciates you hardworking parents

00:00:21.709 --> 00:00:26.714 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and all that you’re doing to try to help
your children find a rich, satisfying life.

00:00:27.798 --> 00:00:31.218 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
As a parent,
I remember the challenge we faced

00:00:31.218 --> 00:00:35.472 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
trying to develop love for Jehovah
in the hearts of our two little boys.

00:00:35.472 --> 00:00:40.394 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We used the tools available,
the Bible, Watchtower articles.

00:00:40.394 --> 00:00:44.565 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Then in 1978,
how thrilled we were to receive

00:00:44.565 --> 00:00:46.609 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
My Book of Bible Stories.

00:00:46.609 --> 00:00:49.069 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What a godsend this proved to be!

00:00:50.321 --> 00:00:52.615 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Over the years, 
the Governing Body has provided

00:00:52.615 --> 00:00:55.868 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
many additional teaching aids
to help our young ones,

00:00:55.868 --> 00:00:59.038 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and we have no intention of stopping there.

00:00:59.038 --> 00:01:02.082 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It is a fact that animated videos

00:01:02.082 --> 00:01:04.418 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
capture the interest of little ones

00:01:04.418 --> 00:01:06.837 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and can be a powerful teaching tool.

00:01:07.588 --> 00:01:11.216 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Hence, it’s my privilege,
on behalf of the Governing Body,

00:01:11.216 --> 00:01:14.845 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to introduce to you a new animated video series

00:01:14.845 --> 00:01:18.432 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
entitled Become Jehovah’s Friend.

00:01:18.432 --> 00:01:23.062 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This is just a preview of what we have
in store for you in the future.

00:01:24.313 --> 00:01:28.067 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Children can learn so much
during their formative years.

00:01:28.067 --> 00:01:30.611 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Lessons they learn at a very young age

00:01:30.611 --> 00:01:34.031 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
can make an impression that lasts a lifetime.

00:01:34.031 --> 00:01:36.617 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It is our prayer that this new series

00:01:36.617 --> 00:01:41.080 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
will help your children
to learn to make God’s heart rejoice.

00:01:41.997 --> 00:01:43.999 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We love you very much.

00:01:43.999 --> 00:01:47.503 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But our love for you is just a reflection

00:01:47.503 --> 00:01:50.923 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of Jehovah’s great love
for you and your little ones.

00:01:50.923 --> 00:01:54.843 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
May they learn, develop, and grow

00:01:54.843 --> 00:01:57.471 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to Become Jehovah’s Friend!

